Package core.data

Class AData

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.data.AData
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AMachineData, DiskData, NetworkData, NetworkInterfaceData
    public abstract class AData
extends Object
    Abstract class for something representing "Data" on our network. This is something which has been read() from a JSON. Beware, null is valid data!
